/products.x-amf-description: This methods receives product information in json format from pim enable and convert it into xml and publish it into Tibco queue.

parameters.name: consumer-id
parameters.description: Unique identifier used to identify consuming application for example, Alfresco

parameters.name: transaction-id
parameters.description: Unique value for each API request sent by consuming application for logging tracing.

parameters.name: client_id
parameters.description: Unique identifier assigned to each consuming app for authentication

parameters.name: client_secret
parameters.description: Client secret sent by consuming app for authentication

transaction-id.description: Transaction Id retunred to consuming application for co-relation of response to request in logs
